ICC T20 World cup 2021 India HD Kit for EA Sports Cricket 07

About the Tournament:

The 2021 ICC Men's T20 World cup is the seventh ICC Men's T20 World cup tournament. It was held in the United Arab Emirates and Oman from 17 October to 14 November 2021. The West Indies are the defending champions.

The tournament was originally scheduled to take place in Australia in 2020, but it was postponed due to the COVID-19 pandemic. In 2021, the tournament was moved to the United Arab Emirates due to concerns over the COVID-19 situation in India.
